data.description: Come tour this Beautiful home -just minutes away from Urbanna-( town nationally known for the Oyster Festival every year). This home is located in a popular sought after Community of Urbanna Harbour- Waterfront at it's finest- Waterfront 150' frontage located on Urbanna Creek-close to Rappahannock River and Chesapeake Bay- Gorgeous views -Stunning home, Large primary suite- walk in closet, updated bathroom with soaking tub and large shower - access to screened porch - step out for your morning coffee- main floor has 4 bedrooms- 4th bedroom being used as office and upstairs bonus room as 5th bedroom or rec room and 3.5 baths. Open floor plan with eat in kitchen over looking great room with gas fireplace, kitchen features corian countertops and wonderful double wall ovens,hardwood floors and tile Family room, gas fireplace, screened porch, 2 car attached garage. New roof- Pinnacle architectural grade shingles, updated bathrooms, plantation shutters throughout- community pool and yacht club available for membership-recent appraisal-$885,000
